cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything.
She looks like a frog, but handles like a dream.
Its' masculinity removes all doubt of the owner's sexuality.
Be one of the few, the proud, space cadets to land on Mars, or something.
This thing zips, zops, zoops, and boops downhill quicker than Bill Cosby's career!
